data.description: Beautiful move in ready Essex built home in the established Pinnacle Ridge community at Lake Carolina. Open layout with beautiful flooring throughout the main level. Main level offers breakfast area, butler's pantry/office flex space, living area, and formal dining room. Open kitchen with granite countertops and plenty of storage space and functionality. Home & backyard are hardwired for speaker system on both floors as well as security. On the second level, unwind in your generously sized primary bedroom with french doors, an oversized sitting area, and 2 walk-in closets. Second level also includes large laundry room with 3 additional bedrooms. Don't miss the rear wrap around grilling deck, bring everyone together around the fire pit in your private fenced in spacious back yard. The speaker system is also wired to the backyard and grilling deck. No worries about front/side yard maintenance which is included in HOA. Double garage with ample parking space. Lake Carolina amenities that are available but not limited to: community security, dog parks, sidewalk/walking/jogging/cycling community, seasonal farmer's markets, playgrounds, private community lake/fishing, and 2 swimming pools! Multi-recreational lifestyle perfect for relaxation. Local YMCA also within Lake Carolina. Gas available. Welcome home! ***up to $3,000 toward closing costs***
